    "shortDescription": "<p>You gift the target with the ability to perfect its actions via mental clarity. On the next attack roll, saving throw, ability check, or sk<i>ill</i> check the target attempts, it rolls twice and takes the more favorable result. For every 5 caster levels you have, the target can roll twice on an additional attack roll, saving throw, ability check, or sk<i>ill</i> check (to a maximum of 5 rolls at 20th level). <i>Hermean potential</i> is countered and dispelled by <i>ill</i> omenAPG, but does not itself counter or dispel <i>ill</i> omen.</p>"
